Version 1.3.11 [2028/02/18]
---------------------------
* event layer is now stable.
* semaphore layer is now stable.
* thread layer added ThreadExit - caller thread destroy - functionality.

+ libs
------
    *

+ source
--------
    * improvements on all layers init functions.

+ template
----------
    * added cmsisRTOS V2 freeRTOS v10.6.2.
    * improvements on ThreadX Queue check size.
    * improvements on ThreadX FreeRTOSCellularPort (handled queue of msg size of 1 byte).
    * improvements on cmsisRTOS V1 Stack Overflow Hook.

+ test
------
    *

+ NOTES
-------
    *


