Version 1.3.6 [2020/12/17]
--------------------------
* thread_main_funct type input type moved from "const void* const" to "void* const" to allow return result from thread (maximum compatibility with different environments).
* thread_main_funct type output type moved from "void*" to "void" (maximum compatibility with different environments).
* for GNUC compiler, added GNUC Major/Minor/Patch version in Version (in accordance with tommRoC library).

